trans-unit.source: Obtains the file locations of Web services discovery documents for use in populating another Web services discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Henter filplassering Web services discovery dokumenter for bruk ved utfylling av en annen Web services discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: The DiscoveryDocumentLinksPattern class inherits from the abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern> class and is employed by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler> class's <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> method, which handles an HTTP request for a discovery document.
trans-unit.target: DiscoveryDocumentLinksPattern klassen arver fra abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern>klasse og ansatt av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler>klassens <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A>metode, som behandler en HTTP-forespørsel for discovery-dokumentet.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern>

trans-unit.source: Normally, none of these classes need to be used directly by a developer.
trans-unit.target: Ingen av disse klassene må vanligvis brukes direkte fra en utvikler.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentLinksPattern"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentLinksPattern"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference"></xref> object for a given discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference"> </xref> objekt for en gitt discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: The concrete <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference> class inherits from the abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference> class.

A <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference> instance contains the location of the .vsdisco file, which is also the file system directory corresponding to the HTTP request passed to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>-forekomsten inneholder plasseringen av filen .vsdisco er også filen systemkatalogen tilsvarer HTTP-forespørselen ble sendt til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>

trans-unit.source: The file-system path of the discovery document.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference"></xref> object that specifies the location of a .vsdisco file.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference"> </xref> objekt som angir plasseringen av en .vsdisco-fil.

trans-unit.source: Gets the file-name pattern to use as a search target.
trans-unit.target: Henter filnavn mønsteret som skal brukes som mål søk.

trans-unit.source: The pattern "*.disco" indicates a Web services discovery document extension, .disco.
trans-unit.target: Mønsteret "* .disco" angir webtjenester discovery dokumentet filtypen .disco.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentSearchPattern> class, on the other hand, indicates a .vsdisco extension.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentSearchPattern>klasse, på den andre siden angir filtypen .vsdisco.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentSearchPattern>
